                p.pb-4 These are the absolute most comparable to Copics in my eyes and much more affordable. Maybe they will make more sets of colors.
            .flex.flex-wrap.mb-4
                img(src="img/reviews-product/review.png", alt="").mr-5.mb-2
                img(src="img/reviews-product/review.png", alt="").mr-5.mb-2
                img(src="img/reviews-product/review.png", alt="")
            hr.border-t-1.border-lightGray
            .flex.justify-between.mt-4.font-sans.font-medium.text-black.text-tiny
                button.flex.items-center
                    +icon("share")
                    span.pl-2 Share
                .flex.items-center
                    p Was this review helpful?
                    p.flex.text-green.pl-4.items-center
                        +icon('like', 'fill-current text-green')
                        span.pl-2 21
                    p.flex.text-red.pl-4.items-center
                        span.pt-1
                            +icon('dislike', 'fill-current text-red')
                        span.pl-2 0

